
XOOPS Cube Legacy

FCKEditor Plugins



############################################## 



PLUGIN KFM - Filemanager
----------------------------------------------

If you want to be able to manage and edit different files (graphics and text)
from FCKeditor,  upload the plugin KFM to your XOOPS Cube Legacy installation:

/common/fckeditor/editor/plugins/ "kfm"

Edit fckeditor configuration file (fckconfig.js)
and add the following code to the last line :

[code]

FCKConfig.Plugins.Add('kfm');

[/code]


Author website and documentation
----------------------------------------------
http://kfm.verens.com/



############################################## 



PLUGIN GOOGLEMAPS
----------------------------------------------

If you want to be able to add a Google Map to a page that you are editing with FCKeditor
upload the plugin Googlemaps to your XOOPS Cube Legacy installation:

/common/fckeditor/editor/plugins/ "googlemaps"

Edit fckeditor configuration file (fckconfig.js)
and add the following code to the last line, separating available languages with comma

[code]

FCKConfig.Plugins.Add( 'googlemaps', 'de,en,es,fr,it,jp') ;
FCKConfig.GoogleMaps_Key = 'ABQIAAAAb9YoJBY0IwbUP_7gmwHPHxT2yXp_ZAY8_ufC3CFXhHIE1NvwkxTIfg4by9dDhRB529vNMdLvhZ-xgw' ;

[/code]


NOTE !
The given GoogleMaps Key is for local test pourpose and will only validate requests from http://localhost



Author website and documentation
----------------------------------------------
http://martinezdelizarrondo.com/googlemaps/



Sign Up for the Google Maps API (free)
----------------------------------------------
http://code.google.com/intl/fr-FR/apis/maps/signup.html



